{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsProtocol"]]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyBackend"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"SettingsRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO11SettingsRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsRef"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyBackend"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"handler"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when they explicitly call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"syntax":"C"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This represents the underlying ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::backend"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/settingsprotocol\/onnotifybackend(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"onNotifyBackend(flags:handler:)","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyBackend"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO11SettingsRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SettingsRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO16SettingsProtocolPAAE15onNotifyBackend5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0B3RefV_AG09ParamSpecM0VtctF","extendedModule":"GIO","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","